               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t17840707-33-punish183" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840707-33-punish183" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840707-33-defend433 t17840707-33-punish183"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>He was humbly recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice ASHURST.</p>
